English

All content in this repository — source code, visual design, logo and seal,
the structure and placement logic of the starfield, the eight-phase
classification system, narrative texts, calligraphic works, and music — is
the exclusive property of the copyright holder.

Without prior written permission, you may not:

  · copy, distribute, transmit, display, or publicly communicate this work
  · create derivative works (including adaptation, translation, or
    modification)
  · reuse any part of it, whether for commercial or non-commercial purposes
  · incorporate any portion of the code or design into a derived project

Public visibility of this repository does not constitute a license.
That the source is visible means it is open to be seen — not to be taken.


